For the PST attack, from Table IX it is evident that the (16,16)1616(16,16) models cannot resist this type of attack, with accuracies on the trigger set declined by more than 20%percent2020\%. The median filter and affine transformations used in PST attacks, lead to severe damage to the small patches because small patches are more easily filtered and transformed. Both the (4,4)44(4,4) and (6,6)66(6,6) models exhibit good robustness against PST attacks.
